segments.text:
I will break the bar of Damascus, and cut off the inhabitant from the valley of Aven, 
and him who holds the scepter from the house of Eden; 
and the people of Syria shall go into captivity to Kir,

For three transgressions of Gaza, yes, for four, I will not turn away its punishment, 
because they carried away captive the whole community, 
to deliver them up to Edom;

For three transgressions of Tyre, yes, for four, I will not turn away its punishment; 
because they delivered up the whole community to Edom, 
and didn’t remember the brotherly covenant;

But I will kindle a fire in the wall of Rabbah, and it will devour its palaces, 
with shouting in the day of battle, 
with a storm in the day of the whirlwind;
